        <br /><br />
        <h3>Do you have a minimum order size?</h3>
        <hr>

        No, we don't have a minimum dollar amount for each order, but each group must be at least 3 people.

        <br /><br />
        <h3>How do I use Derby?</h3>
        <hr>

        Derby’s app is extremely simple to use, and is available on iOS and Android and Web. To order online, visit <a href="http://getderby.co">http://getderby.co</a> and enter your delivery address, then browse featured items for delivery.
        <br /><br />
        &nbsp;&nbsp;1. Select items from the home screen you wish to purchase by clicking the plus icon.
        <br /><br />
        &nbsp;&nbsp;2. Swipe right or click checkout to complete your order.


        <br /><br />
        <h3>When can I use Derby?</h3>
        <hr>

        Derby is available everyday for lunch 10:30am - 2:30pm.

        <br /><br />
        <h3>Where is Derby available?</h3>
        <hr>

        Currently, Derby is only serving Atlanta but we will be expanding to more cities very soon.


        <br /><br />
        <h3>Who makes the deliveries?</h3>
        <hr>

        Our drivers are personally onboarded by our management team to complete deliveries in your city.

        <br /><br />
        <h3>What if I need to contact my driver?</h3>
        <hr>

        You can call your driver at any point during your delivery, directly from the app.

        <br /><br />
        <h3>What should I do if I need to edit my delivery address?</h3>
        <hr>

        If you have not placed your order yet, you can edit the drop-off directly from the home page or the check-out page.
        <br /><br />
        If you've already placed your order and need to change the delivery address, you can call your driver directly from the app.

        <br /><br />
        <h3>What if I need to change my order, or add an item?</h3>
        <hr>

        Call your driver as soon as you realize you need to change the order.


        <br /><br />
        <h3>Is tip required?</h3>
        <hr>

        Tip is not required.. If you would like to leave a tip, you are given the opportunity to add 1, 2, or 3 dollar amount.

        <br /><br />
        <h3>Can I tip my driver with cash?</h3>
        <hr>

        No. Tips are only accepted through the app.

        <br /><br />
        <h3>How do you hire your drivers?</h3>
        <hr>

        All driver are thoroughly vetted, including a background check, in-person interview and test deliveries.

        <br /><br />
        <h3>Can I apply to become a driver?</h3>
        <hr>

        Yes, we would love that! You can submit an application here: <a href="http://getderby.co/drive">http://www.getderby.co/drive</a>

        <br /><br />
        <h3>What if my delivery takes longer than 15 minutes?</h3>
        <hr>

        Depending on the circumstances, we may refund the delivery cost.

        <br /><br />
        <h3>Will my driver bring the meal to my door or inside my office?</h3>
        <hr>

        No, curbside delivery is the quickest and most reliable way for you to connect with your driver.

